The governorship candidate of the All Progressive Congress (APC) in the 2019 gubernatorial election in Sokoto State, Alhaji Ahmed Aliyu Sokoto, has commended the Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) for the rerun election in the state. Ahmed Aliyu said this after he performed his civic rights at about 10:30 am in his polling unit, Tudun Wada ‘A’, located at Magaji Rafi primary school, Sokoto. He also praised the security agencies deployed for the election for professional conduct which he described as one of the best. ALSO READ: Kwara prosecutes 135 sanitation offenders Kwara prosecutes 135 sanitation offenders Sokoto rerun election hitch-free, INEC says as declaration… Amosun: Celebrating a political icon at 62 Group calls for electoral reforms, kicks against… He said, “I am very impressive not only the turnout of people in this polling unit but also coming out so early. “I also commend the security agencies, especially the Nigerian Police Force, Nigerian Security and Civil Defence Corps, Federal Road Safety Corps and others. “I urge everyone to continue to be orderly and ensure the election is crisis free.” Ahmed Aliyu further congratulated INEC for the early distribution of materials and mobilisation which he said helped in the early arrival of the election materials especially in Sokoto metropolis. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NEW MAN MACHINE